illa, Duchess of Cornwall]]; born in Fulham and lived in Hammersmith\n* [[John Mordaunt, 1st Viscount Mordaunt]], royalist; lived and died in Parsons Green\n* [[Joyce Vincent]], born in Hammersmith and raised near Fulham Palace Road.<ref name=how>{{cite news|last=Morley|first=Carol|title=Joyce Carol Vincent: How could this young woman lie dead and undiscovered for almost three years?|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2011/oct/09/joyce-vincent-death-mystery-documentary|accessdate=26 February 2014|newspaper=The Guardian|date=9 October 2011}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{London people}}\n{{LB Hammersmith & Fulham}}\n\n[[Category:People from the London Borough of Hammersmith and Fulham]]\n[[Category:Lists of people from London by borough|Hammersmith and Fulham]]\n", "name_user": "Rodw", "label": "safe", "comment": "Disambiguating links toGeorge Groves(link changed toGeorge Groves (boxer)) usingDisamAssist.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_people_from_the_London_Borough_of_Hammersmith_and_Fulham"}
