asquarterly.org/taxonomy/term/2490 |title= Argentina-China Relations |publisher=Americas Quarterly |accessdate= 18 March 2015}}</ref><ref name=\"autogenerated2\">{{cite web|url= http://www.coha.org/chinese-argentines-and-the-pace-of-cultural-integration/ |title= Chinese Argentines and the Pace of Cultural Integration |accessdate= 18 March 2015}}</ref><ref>[http://www.clarin.com/sociedad/comunidad-china-duplico-ultimos-anos_0_343165728.html Clar\u00edn: As of 2010. Chinese community becomes the fourth largest group of immigrants in Argentina] {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flag|Panama}}||[[Ethnic Chinese in Panama|Chinese-Panamanian]]||135,000||4%||2003<ref name=\"GIO\">{{citation|url=http://www.gio.gov.tw/taiwan-website/5-gp/panama/ch_pa01.htm#3|title=President Chen's State Visit to Panama|publisher=Government Information Office, Republic of China|date=October 2003|accessdate=2007-11-07|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081204231050/http://www.gio.gov.tw/taiwan-website/5-gp/panama/ch_pa01.htm#3|archivedate=4 December 2008|df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"Hua\">{{citation|title=Playing the Panama card&nbsp;\u2013 The China-Taiwan connection|last=Hua|first=Vanessa|periodical=The San Francisco Chronicle|url=http://www.journalismfellowships.org/stories/panama/panama_chinataiwan.htm|date=2002-06-23|accessdate=2007-11-07}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flag|Cuba}}||[[Chinese Cuban]]||114,240||1%||2008<ref>CIA World Factbook. Cuba. 15 May 2008. <https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/cu.html>.</ref>\n|-\n|{{flag|Jamaica}}||[[Chinese Jamaicans]]||72,000|| ||--<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.joshuaproject.net/peopctry.php?rop3=103691&rog3=JM|title=Han Chinese, Hakka in Jamaica|author=Joshua Project|website=Joshuaproject.net|accessdate=18 March 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flag|Mexico}}||[[Chinese immigration to Mexico|Chinese Mexican]]||70,000||nil||2008<!---ref name=\"Rodriguez\"/ This isn't a real citation, so I'm adding a citation needed--->{{citation n